# Monorepo Structure

## Active Repository Shape

- `applications/backend`: NestJS API.
- `applications/frontend`: Vite + React application.
- `packages/aor-common/*`: shared libraries (`adapters`, `domain`, `logger`, `ports`, `types`, `utils`).
- `packages/aor-drizzle`: Drizzle schema and database helpers.
- `packages/aor-questionnaires`: questionnaire catalog package.
- `packages/aor-scoring`: scoring package.

## Dependency Boundaries

- Applications may import from packages.
- Packages must never import from applications.
- Frontend code must stay free of backend-only dependencies such as Nest modules or `@aor/drizzle`.
- Prefer reusing an existing package or layer before introducing a new top-level folder or package.
